WEBVTT

00:25.450 --> 00:27.250
Nice moves, kid.

00:27.400 --> 00:30.990
Nice moves?
Rainbow Dash thinks I've got--

00:33.700 --> 00:35.440
nice moves!

00:39.420 --> 00:44.420
Season 3 | Episode 6
Sleepless in Ponyville

00:46.300 --> 00:50.100
